88
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:34,220
We could get a platinum
if we took it to the capital!

89
00:02:34,220 --> 00:02:35,390
What?!

90
00:02:36,050 --> 00:02:38,260
That's enough to build a fine house!

91
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,680
Yeah!

92
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:44,480
The Kurokoma boss is looking for a legendary
white boar to display in his storefront,

93
00:02:44,890 --> 00:02:47,270
so he posted a reward for one.

94
00:02:47,270 --> 00:02:49,440
He can't put it on display!

95
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:53,110
White boars are divine messengers.

96
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:59,700
Kin'emon!

97
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:01,490
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!

98
