Ahh... Don't cry! Oh, wait...

182
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:45,830
Crematorium

Flower
Capital

183
00:03:45,830 --> 00:03:49,170
I guess you can cry at a funeral.

184
00:03:49,170 --> 00:03:50,420
What's the matter?

185
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:56,380
We finished the cremation
and were about to gather his bones,

186
00:03:56,380 --> 00:03:58,050
but then that man...!

187
00:03:58,050 --> 00:04:03,060
He started cooking oden
using my father's pyre!

188
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:12,060
It seems like Lord Oden
is completely incapable of sailing.

189
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:17,650
This was the thirty-eighth time he has
tried to illegally leave the country.

190
00:04:17,650 --> 00:04:20,530
And he returned in one piece?

191
00:04:20,530 --> 00:04:25,750
I suspect you are familiar with the details,
but allow me to briefly recount his life.

192
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:28,790
Kozuki Sukiyaki

Shogun of Wano
(Oden's Father)

193
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,790
Before he was even a year old,

194
00:04:29,330 --> 00:04:31,080
he sent his nanny flying.

195
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:34,090
When he was two,
he caught two rabbits at once.

196
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:38,550
At four, he hurled a boulder
at a bear and knocked it out.

197
00:04:38,970 --> 00:04:43,220
At age six, he spent all his time
frittering away the treasury at pleasure halls.

198
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:47,020
When he was eight, 
he went alone to a gambling den

199
00:04:47,020 --> 00:04:51,730
and started a brawl with some
hot-tempered gamblers.

200
00:04:51,730 --> 00:04:54,440
When he was nine,
he was blacklisted by the yakuza.

201
00:04:55,070 --> 00:05:00,320
He repaid them by setting their
gambling den ablaze and starting a gang war.

202
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:02,570
After that, he was arrested for assault.

203
00:05:02,990 --> 00:05:04,950
That was at the age of ten.

204
00:05:05,370 --> 00:05:10,370
He served time at the quarry,
which is when his skills blossomed.

205
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:14,170
He climbed the ranks
and became a master stonemason!

206
00:05:14,590 --> 00:05:16,920
It must be his Kozuki blood!

207
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:21,970
He returned to the streets a changed man!

208
00:05:22,550 --> 00:05:24,430
When Lord Oden was fourteen,

209
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:26,470
a drought struck the capital.

210
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:29,930
He could not just let people
suffer as the wells dried,

211
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:34,060
so he changed the river's course
and made it flow to the capital.

212
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:38,230
But it caused a massive flood...

213
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:41,110
resulting in another arrest warrant!

214
00:05:42,450 --> 00:05:48,870
He attempted to flee from
the country through the channel...

215
00:05:50,710 --> 00:05:52,960
though he failed quite miserably!

216
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:58,090
At fifteen, he strong-armed the master of
a mountain temple and stayed hidden there.

217
00:05:58,710 --> 00:06:04,890
He brought back women from the capital
every night and formed a harem!

218
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:09,720
That makes him sound like
some kind of monster.

219
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:15,100
I should add that all those women
were always free to leave.

220
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:18,730
But there were some who could not abide this!

221
00:06:19,570 --> 00:06:23,740
They were those women's
boyfriends, parents, and husbands!

222
00:06:24,450 --> 00:06:26,950
A group of strapping samurai
accompanied them!

223
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:34,210
Lord Oden welcomed
their challenge and fought back!

224
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:37,920
This was known as the Harem War!

225
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:45,180
The Hyogoro Family intervened to stop
them all, and a massive brawl took place!

226
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:46,260
Enough!

227
00:06:48,850 --> 00:06:51,270
Lord Oden is now eighteen years old.

228
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,730
He remains recalcitrant even now.

229
00:06:53,730 --> 00:06:56,150
That is all I have to report.

230
00:06:56,150 --> 00:07:00,270
Save your commentary
and deliver this to Oden.

