293
00:07:45,490 --> 00:07:51,330
Hyogoro 
"the Flower"


Man of Chivalry, 
Flower Capital

294
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:51,330
But do not fight him one-on-one.

295
00:07:51,330 --> 00:07:55,080
